Major
The major market is based on the overall performance indicator in accordance with criteria such as the virtual asset's market liquidity, market captilization and project integrity. This market has more stability in investment compared to other markets. The market may be altered time to time.
General
The following virtual asset is not registered as a major, new, or investment warning. This market may fluctuate drastically due to lower stability in investment compared to major market. The virtual asset in this market can be changed to major or investment warning.
